                  </hi> On Friday evening, the 3rd of Sept., about a quarter to six o'clock, I took the prisoners into custody, on Saffron-hill—Cain had three planes under his arm, trying to conceal them by putting them under his coat—I went up and asked what he had got—he said. "Nothing"—he after<lb></lb>wards said he had got three planes, produced them, and said Perkins gave them to him—Perkins immediately ran away.</p>
               <p>
